            <h1>Admission Information</h1>
            <p>Find all the information you need about our admission process, including deadlines, requirements, and how to apply.</p>
            <h2>Admission Deadlines</h2>
            <p>Our admission deadlines for the upcoming academic year are as follows:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Early Decision: December 1</li>
                <li>Regular Decision: March 1</li>
                <li>Late Applications: May 1</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Requirements</h2>
            <p>To apply, you must meet the following requirements:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Completed application form</li>
                <li>High school transcripts</li>
                <li>Standardized test scores (SAT/ACT)</li>
                <li>Letters of recommendation</li>
                <li>Personal statement</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>How to Apply</h2>
            <p>Follow these steps to complete your application:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Fill out the online application form.</li>
                <li>Upload your transcripts and test scores.</li>
                <li>Submit your letters of recommendation.</li>
                <li>Write and submit your personal statement.</li>
                <li>Pay the application fee.</li>
            </ol>
